title: Kijitora Neko no Koume-san
original_name: キジトラ猫の小梅さん
sinopse: This cat name is "Koume," but a lot of people call her "Koume-san" like Miss Koume. She understand exactly what people say and people's mind. She is so kind and cute. Koume lives with a single mom and her son, and another cat, name Koyuki.
